iv> <div class=\"d-flex flex-fill flex-column py-4\"> <span class=\"sub-heading color-white py-3\"> Prominent vs Common Cards </span> <p class=\"paragraph pb-4\"> We also designed each information module of the movie page in a way that can be reused for the to show information about cast & crew, production companies and theatres as well. </p> <div class=\"d-flex\"> <div class=\"d-flex flex-fill flex-column pr-4\"> <div class=\"card p-4 d-flex flex-fill mb-4\"> </div> <div class=\"card p-4 d-flex flex-fill mb-4\"> </div> <div class=\"card p-4 d-flex flex-fill mb-4\"> </div> </div> <div class=\"d-flex flex-fill flex-column\"> <div class=\"card p-4 d-flex flex-fill mb-4\"> </div> <div class=\"card p-4 d-flex flex-fill mb-4\"> </div><div class=\"card p-4 d-flex flex-fill mb-4\"> </div> </div> </div> <div class=\"d-flex flex-fill flex-column\"> <div class=\"d-flex secondary-heading color-white py-4\"> <span class=\"pr-3\">The</span> <span class=\"highlight-orange px-1\">Interactions</span> </div> <p class=\"paragraph pb-3\"> As our principle clearly highlighted to give the user minimal effort, we focussed to give swiftness, better correlation to the eyes and less stress for the muscles during the interaction with the elements in our product. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class=\"d-flex flex-fill pb-5\"> <div class=\"d-flex pt-3\"> <span class=\"d-flex rectangle\"> </span> <span class=\"sub-heading pl-3 color-white\">FEB 2018</span> </div> <div class=\"d-flex flex-column\"> <div class=\"d-flex flex-column\"> <div class=\"py-3\"> <span class=\"sub-heading py-2\">Identifying</span> <div class=\"d-flex heading pb-4\"> <span class=\"pr-3\">The</span> <span class=\"highlight-orange px-1\">Necessary Phase</span> </div> </div> </div> <div class=\"d-flex\"> <div class=\"d-flex flex-column flex-fill px-3\"> <span class=\"sub-heading color-white py-3\"> Add to watchlist </span> <p class=\"paragraph pb-4\"> This action notifies the user about the updates of the movie 